Surveys Analysis
Technology Utilisation Results
We initially studied the technology utilization patterns of the patient using an adapted version of a technology use questionnaire (Q1) [15]. The median (Q1–Q3) of participants who reported daily use of the technology was 18 (1319) (Fig. 3). Only five patients have another frequency of use. While specific health information searches and apps


